1.Open Ubuntu Software Center
2. Install "winetricks" , logmein-hamachi
3. download StrongHold crusader from cloud. https://cloud.mail.ru/public/L6Ko/oVvMTfnQp
4. Extract archive.
5. Go to StrongholdCrusaderHD / prefix / drive_c / Program Files / Stronghold Crusader HD / Stronghold Crusader.exe
6. https://help.ubuntu.com/community/Hamachi
  a. sudo add-apt-repository -y ppa:webupd8team/haguichi
  b.sudo apt update
  c.sudo apt install -y haguichi
